[h3 className:"imageCaption"]**Summary for land development**

- When comparing **Expansion vs. New Settlements**, there is not a major difference in total land take - though the location of development is very different. In the Expansion scenario, developments sprawl around existing urban areas, whereas in New Settlements there are new high density centres.
- When comparing **Grey vs. Green**, the Green scenario takes less land because it assumes a higher density of all new development.
[/h3]


